```plantuml
@startuml oovk_dataengg-covid19-aws
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor DataEngineer

rectangle "Jupyter Notebook" as Jupyter #lightyellow {
  rectangle "covid19_project.ipynb" as Notebook
}

rectangle "AWS S3" as S3 #aliceblue

rectangle "AWS Athena" as Athena #lightsteelblue

rectangle "Pandas\nDataFrames" as Pandas #lightcoral

rectangle "Amazon Redshift" as Redshift #palegreen

' ========== Interactions ==========
DataEngineer --> Notebook : initiate ETL process

' Data extraction
Notebook --> Athena : query datasets\nfrom AWS Open Data
Athena --> Pandas : load query results\ninto DataFrames

' Data transformation
Notebook --> Pandas : transform and clean data\nmerge datasets\nfeature engineering

' Data storage
Pandas --> S3 : save transformed data\nas CSV files

' Data modeling
Notebook --> Pandas : create dimensional model\nfact and dimension tables

' Load data to warehouse
Notebook --> Redshift : execute SQL create table\nfrom DataFrame schema
Pandas --> Redshift : load data into\nRedshift tables

@enduml
```